          <h2 class="homepage-header">Get Involved with iSENSE</h2> <br />
          <div class="homepage-text">
            <p class="involvement">
              For more information, please contact Fred Martin (<a href="mailto:fredm@cs.uml.edu">fredm@cs.uml.edu</a>) and Samantha Michalka (<a href="mailto:samantha@machinescience.org">samantha@machinescience.org</a>). We hold workshops for teachers to learn how to use iSENSE in the classroom, and for students to learn about scientific data collection and analysis. We will also come to your school with the tools and resources necessary to use iSENSE.
